rows.label: qst300304_msg0001
rows.name: Are you the one in charge here?

rows.label: qst300304_msg0002
rows.name: No, that'd be the boy.

rows.label: qst300304_msg0005
rows.name:
You're so young! But I can see
that everyone here respects you
a lot. I like that.

rows.label: qst300304_msg0006
rows.name: I'm Alicia. I'm from Superbia.

rows.label: qst300304_msg0007
rows.name: What would you like to know?

rows.label: qst300304_msg0051
rows.name: What should I ask about?

rows.label: qst300304_msg0052
rows.name: Her personal motivations

rows.label: qst300304_msg0053
rows.name: Her strongest skills

rows.label: qst300304_msg0054
rows.name: Where she sees herself in five years

rows.label: qst300304_msg0055
rows.name: Nothing in particular

rows.label: qst300304_msg0101
rows.name:
Well, I've been putting out feelers
here and there, and I have to say...

rows.label: qst300304_msg0102
rows.name:
Not a bad word was ever said
about the Hræsvelgr Mercs. They've
an excellent reputation.

rows.label: qst300304_msg0103
rows.name:
I don't have combat experience
myself, but I believe that I'm more than
capable of helping from the sidelines.

rows.label: qst300304_msg0104
rows.name: You must have other reasons, no?

rows.label: qst300304_msg0105
rows.name:
Well...to be frank with you, there was
nothing truly engaging for me back in
Alba Margen.

rows.label: qst300304_msg0106
rows.name:
Everyone there is so sour-faced and
miserable and always in a hurry...
That's why I left Superbia.

rows.label: qst300304_msg0201
rows.name:
Oh, nothing that stands out in any
special capacity...

rows.label: qst300304_msg0202
rows.name:
But if I had to pick, I'd say it's my
forward-thinking attitude.

rows.label: qst300304_msg0203
rows.name: That's a really good attitude to have!

rows.label: qst300304_msg0204
rows.name: You think so? I'm glad.

rows.label: qst300304_msg0205
rows.name:
Ah, I'm also an excellent cook!
Give me any drink and I'll rustle
up the perfect meal to match it!

rows.label: qst300304_msg0301
rows.name: I haven't really thought that far ahead...

rows.label: qst300304_msg0302
rows.name:
I believe that if I'm happy in the here
and now, then the future is sure to be
just as bright.

rows.label: qst300304_msg0303
rows.name: Does that apply only to yourself?

rows.label: qst300304_msg0304
rows.name:
No, no, not at all. That would be
very lonely, wouldn't it? If I were
the only one who were happy...

rows.label: qst300304_msg0305
rows.name:
I always do my very best to make the
people around me smile. Of that you
can be sure.

rows.label: qst300304_msg0401
rows.name:
All right, I think we can wrap
it up there.

rows.label: qst300304_msg0402
rows.name:
We'll make our final decision shortly.
You can go.

rows.label: qst300304_msg0403
rows.name:
All right. I hope you choose the right
person for the job!

rows.label: qst300304_msg0404
rows.name: Right, I'm calling in the next one.

rows.label: qst300304_msg0501
rows.name: Anything else you want to ask?
